Limit Break

By using specialized materials, limit breaks can be performed on gear, raising both their level limit and their CP.
* Limit breaks do not exist for unrealized BT weapons and unrealized 7★ armor.


When you have enough materials, select Limit Break on the material selection screen.




Different materials are needed when performing a limit break on different types of equipment.

Equipment used as material to enhance another piece of equipment will be consumed in the process, and any enhancements on that material will be lost as well.

Please keep these factors in mind and consider carefully what to enhance and what to use as material.
